lay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871840/extras/0cac1a0a32d2f5fc012319228e5f2051.poster.avif?t=1721137199\" width=640 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871840/extras/0cac1a0a32d2f5fc012319228e5f2051.webm?t=1721137199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871840/extras/0cac1a0a32d2f5fc012319228e5f2051.mp4?t=1721137199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
